<feature
      id="org.eclipse.papyrus.designer.basic.feature"
      label="%featureName"
      version="0.7.0"
      provider-name="%providerName">

   <description>
      The Papyrus Designer tool suite is a component based design methodology
based
on
- A profile derived from a flexible component model (FCM) with
- extensible port definitions (kind)
- extensible set of connector types and implementations
- extensible set of container services
- A library of predefined port kinds
- A library of connector types along with their implementations
- The tool chain supporting a set of model-to-model transformation
(connector and container expansion)
- A C++ code generator
- A Java code generator
- CDT support, i.e. the generation of a CDT project from the
model
   </description>

